data.title: Ken Wharton 1953 statistics
data.meta_description: Discover Ken Wharton's 1953 Formula 1 World Championship stats, including detailed performance progression throughout the season.
data.text: In the 1953 Formula 1 season Ken Wharton drove a total of 5 races for Cooper. From the total of 5 races, Ken managed to finish on a 7th place during the 1953 Swiss Grand Prix. If we take a look at the races, where Wharton didn't finish, this happend in 2 occasions. The best result for Ken during qualifying was at the 1953 Swiss Grand Prix as 9th fastest.
